@startuml
class Book {
  -title: String
  -author: String
  -category: String
  -isBorrowed: Boolean
  +borrow()
  +returnBook()
}

class Member {
  -name: String
  -memberID: int
  -borrowedBooks: List
  +borrowBook()
  +returnBook()
  +viewHistory()
}

class Librarian {
  -name: String
  +addBook()
  +removeBook()
  +updateBook()
  +manageMember()
}

class Transaction {
  -transactionID: int
  -date: Date
  -fineAmount: float
  +calculateFine()
}

Book "1" -- "*" Member : borrowed by
Librarian --> Book : manages
Librarian --> Member : manages
Member --> Transaction
Book --> Transaction
@enduml
